{
  "stem": "5388.7",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I liked it so much, I-- and I did sing it in the camps.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I sang it after the war.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I used to entertain some of the friends that used to come and knew Yiddish, so I used to sing it for them.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I like that song.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It was a-- because it's partly kind of a potpourri of a number of songs like-- that are in there, you know.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Folk songs.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Ah, the crowd was clapping, you know.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were enjoying it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Oh, yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, sure.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Sure.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I liked that song.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I knew it by heart.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I knew the whole song from the beginning to end, and I understood all of the connections and the cultural annotations of the speak, and the-- the-- the finer points on it.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So, yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I enjoyed it very much.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yoshke goes away, and that's it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That's the end of it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And now she--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because it says-- the song says-- [SINGING IN YIDDISH] I went to the train to accompany-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] which is her friend, Yoshke, to-- and I stayed at the station.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So in other words, she's accompanying here the soldier who goes to the army.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He's being drafted.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And now, he's-- keep in mind, we are talking now in the Czarist army before the First World War.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, the parting.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That's right.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "What's that?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It's a happy song.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And it's-- it is-- they kind of know they are parting, and the train leaves and that's it.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, but in-- for that one to sing, I would have to refresh my recollection.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I did it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I got it only yesterday from a copy of-- some of it, I remember by heart.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
